      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/equiv-input-001",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation input parameters demonstrated equivalent to experimental conditions used in validation.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency of input parameters is not formally assessed at MRL 2. Qualitative alignment between simulation and experimental inputs has been confirmed through engineering judgment, but quantitative equivalency metrics are not computed within this assessment."
