    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements for Class II devices. CFD predictions of hemolysis index are within 20% of experimental measurements across all operating points. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device COU.",
